(1865, 'sea captain mutiny sword prime minister sailing silver ship duke mermaid pirate soldier battle swashbuckler aftercreditsstinger 3d', 'Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides', 'Captain Jack Sparrow crosses paths with a woman from his past, and he\'s not sure if it\'s love -- or if she\'s a ruthless con artist who\'s using him to find the fabled Fountain of Youth. When she forces him aboard the Queen Anne\'s Revenge, the ship of the formidable pirate Blackbeard, Jack finds himself on an unexpected adventure in which he doesn\'t know who to fear more: Blackbeard or the woman from his past.', 'en', 135.413856, 6.4, 'Adventure Action Fantasy', '', 'Johnny Depp Penélope Cruz Ian McShane'),
(1874, 'jail guard prison cell south africa apartheid nelson mandela escape xenophobia', 'Goodbye Bafana', 'The true story of a white South African racist whose life was profoundly altered by the black prisoner he guarded for twenty years. The prisoner\'s name was Nelson Mandela.', 'en', 12.257654, 7, 'History Drama', '', 'Joseph Fiennes Dennis Haysbert Diane Kruger'),
(1878, 'gonzo journalist sweaty face fake identity wedding chapel grapefruit cadillac convertible gibberish corvette stingray police convention', 'Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas', 'The hallucinogenic misadventures of sportswriter Raoul Duke and his Samoan lawyer, Dr. Gonzo, on a three-day romp from Los Angeles to Las Vegas. Motoring across the Mojave Desert on the way to Sin City, Duke and his purple haze passenger ingest a cornucopia of drugs ranging from acid to ether.', 'en', 44.511363, 7.2, 'Adventure Drama Comedy', 'Terry Gilliam', 'Johnny Depp Benicio del Toro Tobey Maguire'),
(1880, 'guerrilla colorado invasion anti-communism near future red army', 'Red Dawn', 'It is the mid-1980s. From out of the sky, Soviet and Cuban troops begin landing on the football field of a Colorado high school. In seconds, the paratroops have attacked the school and sent a group of teenagers fleeing into the mountains. Armed only with hunting rifles, pistols and bows and arrows, the teens struggles to survive the bitter winter and Soviet KGB patrols hunting for them.', 'en', 11.743085, 6.4, 'Action Thriller', 'John Milius', 'Patrick Swayze C. Thomas Howell Lea Thompson'),
(1883, 'islam new york prison assassination ku klux klan muslim police brutality beach koran jail guard prison cell bible biography martin luther king nation of islam civil rights movement  mekka pilgrimage cabriolet police historical figure malcolm x', 'Malcolm X', 'The biopic of the controversial and influential Black Nationalist leader.', 'en', 19.822791, 7.2, 'Drama History', '', 'Denzel Washington Angela Bassett Albert Hall'),
