(1907, 'hippie exotic island beach map group dynamics shark attack leader thailand community backpacker delusion marijuana youth shark extramarital affair', 'The Beach', 'Twenty-something Richard travels to Thailand and finds himself in possession of a strange map. Rumours state that it leads to a solitary beach paradise, a tropical bliss - excited and intrigued, he sets out to find it.', 'en', 41.362082, 6.3, 'Drama Adventure Romance Thriller', 'Danny Boyle', 'Leonardo DiCaprio Guillaume Canet Tilda Swinton'),
