(3021, 'suicide new york hotel fire hotel room wife husband relationship suicide attempt window door haunted house research ghost world painting telephone loss of daughter blood', '1408', 'A man who specializes in debunking paranormal occurrences checks into the fabled room 1408 in the Dolphin Hotel. Soon after settling in, he confronts genuine terror.', 'en', 35.169779, 6.5, 'Horror Thriller', '', 'John Cusack Samuel L. Jackson Mary McCormack'),
