(3059, 'usa naivety intolerance mill marriage wedding massacre protestant silent film multiple storylines reformer saved from hanging jesus', 'Intolerance', 'The story of a poor young woman, separated by prejudice from her husband and baby, is interwoven with tales of intolerance from throughout history.', 'en', 3.232447, 7.4, 'Drama', '', 'Lillian Gish Mae Marsh Robert Harron'),
