(3093, 'male nudity sex legs soho london playing god jacuzzi', 'Basic Instinct 2', 'Novelist Catherine Tramell is once again in trouble with the law, and Scotland Yard appoints psychiatrist Dr. Michael Glass to evaluate her. Though, like Detective Nick Curran before him, Glass is entranced by Tramell and lured into a seductive game.', 'en', 13.483387, 4.6, 'Crime Mystery Thriller', '', 'Sharon Stone David Morrissey Charlotte Rampling'),
