(3597, 'secret blackmail fisherman police high school cover-up friends revenge murder pageant slasher teenager killer', 'I Know What You Did Last Summer', 'As they celebrate their high school graduation, four friends are involved in a hit-and-run accident when their car hits and apparently kills a pedestrian on an isolated roadway. They dispose of the body and vow to keep the incident a secret, a year later somebody starts sending them letters bearing the warning \"I Know What You Did Last Summer.\"', 'en', 27.654472, 5.6, 'Horror Thriller Mystery', '', 'Jennifer Love Hewitt Sarah Michelle Gellar Ryan Phillippe'),
