(4032, 'neighbor child killed by animal writing class makeup artist bee sting camper cosmetologist tree climbing death in childbirth tuba motor home bee attack', 'My Girl', 'Vada Sultenfuss is obsessed with death. Her mother is dead, and her father runs a funeral parlor. She is also in love with her English teacher, and joins a poetry class over the summer just to impress him. Thomas J., her best friend, is \"allergic to everything\", and sticks with Vada despite her hangups. When Vada\'s father hires Shelly, and begins to fall for her, things take a turn to the worse...', 'en', 20.935169, 7, 'Comedy Drama Family', '', 'Anna Chlumsky Macaulay Culkin Dan Aykroyd'),
