(9392, 'mutant expedition cave darkness rope climbing bestie appalachia friends female protagonist survival horror', 'The Descent', 'After a tragic accident, six friends reunite for a caving expedition. Their adventure soon goes horribly wrong when a collapse traps them deep underground and they find themselves pursued by bloodthirsty creatures. As their friendships deteriorate, they find themselves in a desperate struggle to survive the creatures and each other.', 'en', 23.413188, 6.8, 'Adventure Horror', '', 'Shauna Macdonald Natalie Mendoza Alex Reid'),
(9398, 'male model time magazine fashion show fashion model fictional awards show lincoln assassination coal mine', 'Zoolander', 'Clear the runway for Derek Zoolander, VH1\'s three-time male model of the year. His face falls when hippie-chic \"he\'s so hot right now\" Hansel scooters in to steal this year\'s award. The evil fashion guru Mugatu seizes the opportunity to turn Derek into a killing machine. Its a well-designed conspiracy and only with the help of Hansel and a few well-chosen accessories can Derek make the world safe.', 'en', 38.0958, 6.1, 'Comedy', '', 'Ben Stiller Owen Wilson Christine Taylor'),
