(9416, 'prison diamant liberation of prisoners transport of prisoners interview arrest', 'Money Talks', 'Money Talks is a 1997 American comedy film directed by Brett Ratner. Sought by police and criminals, a small-time huckster makes a deal with a TV newsman for protection.', 'en', 7.615653, 5.9, 'Action Adventure Comedy', '', 'Chris Tucker Charlie Sheen Heather Locklear'),
