(9437, 'washington d.c. covered investigation investigation north carolina missing person', 'Kiss the Girls', 'Forensic psychologist Alex Cross travels to North Carolina and teams with escaped kidnap victim Kate McTiernan to hunt down \"Casanova,\" a serial killer who abducts strong-willed women and forces them to submit to his demands. The trail leads to Los Angeles, where the duo discovers that the psychopath may not be working alone.', 'en', 18.913, 6.2, 'Drama Mystery Thriller Crime', '', 'Morgan Freeman Ashley Judd Cary Elwes'),
