(17663, 'based on novel brother sister relationship canada village love school miniseries best friend orphan historical kids redhead girl', 'Anne of Green Gables', 'At the turn of the century on Prince Edward Island, Matthew Cuthbert and his sister Marilla decide to take on an orphan boy as help for their farm. But they get an unexpected jolt when they\'re mistakenly sent a girl instead: Anne Shirley. Anne\'s a dreamer with an unusual point of view, far removed from Marilla\'s pragmatic ways, and it\'s only on trial that Marilla agrees to keep Anne.', 'en', 8.772574, 8.2, 'Drama Family', 'Kevin Sullivan', 'Megan Follows Colleen Dewhurst Richard Farnsworth'),
