(25975, 'obsession camcorder crush dream girl', 'My Date with Drew', 'Ever since the second grade when he first saw her in E.T. The Extraterrestrial, Brian Herzlinger has had a crush on Drew Barrymore. Now, 20 years later he\'s decided to try to fulfill his lifelong dream by asking her for a date. There\'s one small problem: She\'s Drew Barrymore and he\'s, well, Brian Herzlinger, a broke 27-year-old aspiring filmmaker from New Jersey.', 'en', 1.929883, 6.3, 'Documentary', 'Brian Herzlinger', 'Drew Barrymore Brian Herzlinger Corey Feldman'),
