(27578, 'tattoo martial arts sniper island mercenary bridge rescue escape church drug blade ensemble cast duringcreditsstinger', 'The Expendables', 'Barney Ross leads a band of highly skilled mercenaries including knife enthusiast Lee Christmas, a martial arts expert, heavy weapons specialist, demolitionist, and a loose-cannon sniper. When the group is commissioned by the mysterious Mr. Church to assassinate the dictator of a small South American island, Barney and Lee visit the remote locale to scout out their opposition and discover the true nature of the conflict engulfing the city.', 'en', 77.580661, 6, 'Thriller Adventure Action', '', 'Sylvester Stallone Jason Statham Dolph Lundgren'),
