(39845, 'independent film', 'Love Ranch', 'Story of a couple that starts the first legal brothel in Nevada and a boxer they own a piece of.', 'en', 5.000126, 6, 'Drama', 'Taylor Hackford', 'Helen Mirren Joe Pesci Sergio Peris-Mencheta'),
