(59967, 'suicide assassin drug addiction future time travel dystopia retirement boy murder organized crime tragedy execution violence criminal drug addict contract killer neo-noir', 'Looper', 'In the futuristic action thriller Looper, time travel will be invented but it will be illegal and only available on the black market. When the mob wants to get rid of someone, they will send their target 30 years into the past where a looper, a hired gun, like Joe is waiting to mop up. Joe is getting rich and life is good until the day the mob decides to close the loop, sending back Joe\'s future self for assassination.', 'en', 46.377628, 6.6, 'Action Thriller Science Fiction', '', 'Joseph Gordon-Levitt Bruce Willis Emily Blunt'),
(59968, 'brother sister relationship sister sister relationship family clan idealist duringcreditsstinger', 'Our Idiot Brother', 'Everybody has the sibling who is always just a little bit behind the curve when it comes to getting his life together. For sisters Liz, Miranda and Natalie, that person is their perennially upbeat brother Ned, an erstwhile organic farmer whose willingness to rely on the honesty of mankind is a less-than-optimum strategy for a tidy, trouble-free existence. Ned may be utterly lacking in common sense, but he is their brother and so, after his girlfriend dumps him and boots him off the farm, his sisters once again come to his rescue. As Liz, Miranda and Natalie each take a turn at housing Ned, their brother\'s unfailing commitment to honesty creates more than a few messes in their comfortable routines. But as each of their lives begins to unravel, Ned\'s family comes to realize that maybe, in believing and trusting the people around him, Ned isn\'t such an idiot after all.', 'en', 15.688439, 5.9, 'Comedy Drama', '', 'Paul Rudd Elizabeth Banks Zooey Deschanel'),
(59981, '', 'Legends of Oz: Dorothy\'s Return', 'Dorothy wakes up in post-tornado Kansas, only to be whisked back to Oz to try to save her old friends the Scarecrow, the Lion, the Tin Man and Glinda from a devious new villain, the Jester. Wiser the owl, Marshal Mallow, China Princess and Tugg the tugboat join Dorothy on her latest magical journey through the colorful landscape of Oz to restore order and happiness to Emerald City.', 'en', 6.682006, 5.9, 'Animation Music Family', '', 'Lea Michele Dan Aykroyd Patrick Stewart'),
(60304, 'witch black magic steampunk good vs evil troll extreme violence violence witchcraft evil witch hunt witch hunter evil witch duringcreditsstinger hansel and gretel guns 3d', 'Hansel & Gretel: Witch Hunters', 'After getting a taste for blood as children, Hansel and Gretel have become the ultimate vigilantes, hell-bent on retribution. Now, unbeknownst to them, Hansel and Gretel have become the hunted, and must face an evil far greater than witches... their past.', 'en', 53.02787, 5.7, 'Fantasy Horror Action', '', 'Jeremy Renner Gemma Arterton Famke Janssen'),
