(76494, 'based on novel adoption pregnant miscarriage expectant father pregnant wife vomiting expecting twins open air cinema giving birth', 'What to Expect When You\'re Expecting', 'Challenges of impending parenthood turn the lives of five couples upside down. Two celebrities are unprepared for the surprise demands of pregnancy; hormones wreak havoc on a baby-crazy author, while her husband tries not to be outdone by his father, who\'s expecting twins with his young trophy wife; a photographer\'s husband isn\'t sure about his wife\'s adoption plans; a one-time hook-up results in a surprise pregnancy for rival food-truck owners.', 'en', 27.009723, 5.8, 'Romance Comedy Drama', '', 'Cameron Diaz Jennifer Lopez Elizabeth Banks'),
(76617, 'sequel gore leatherface slasher chainsaw aftercreditsstinger duringcreditsstinger', 'Texas Chainsaw 3D', 'A young woman learns that she has inherited a Texas estate from her deceased grandmother. After embarking on a road trip with friends to uncover her roots, she finds she is the sole owner of a lavish, isolated Victorian mansion. But her newfound wealth comes at a price as she stumbles upon a horror that awaits her in the mansion’s dank cellars.', 'en', 26.497025, 5.3, 'Horror Thriller', '', 'Alexandra Daddario Dan Yeager Bill Moseley'),
(76640, 'sheriff small town hostage prisoner fbi border escape car chase convoy machine gun neo-western', 'The Last Stand', 'Ray Owens is sheriff of the quiet US border town of Sommerton Junction after leaving the LAPD following a bungled operation. Following his escape from the FBI, a notorious drug baron, his gang, and a hostage are heading toward Sommerton Junction where the police are preparing to make a last stand to intercept them before they cross the border. Owens is reluctant to become involved but ultimately joins in with the law enforcement efforts', 'en', 43.882857, 5.7, 'Action Crime Thriller', '', 'Arnold Schwarzenegger Forest Whitaker Rodrigo Santoro'),
(76649, 'gladiator arena gladiator fight lava roman forbidden love natural disaster epic disaster slave town in panic vulcan volcanic eruption pompeii 3d', 'Pompeii', 'Set in 79 A.D., POMPEII tells the epic story of Milo, a slave turned invincible gladiator who finds himself in a race against time to save his true love Cassia, the beautiful daughter of a wealthy merchant who has been unwillingly betrothed to a corrupt Roman Senator. As Mount Vesuvius erupts in a torrent of blazing lava, Milo must fight his way out of the arena in order to save his beloved as the once magnificent Pompeii crumbles around him.', 'en', 50.561849, 5.2, 'Action Adventure History Romance Drama', 'Paul W.S. Anderson', 'Kit Harington Carrie-Anne Moss Emily Browning'),
