(78698, 'whale alaska aftercreditsstinger duringcreditsstinger greenpeace animal protection', 'Big Miracle', 'Based on an inspiring true story, a small-town news reporter (Krasinski) and a Greenpeace volunteer (Barrymore) enlist the help of rival superpowers to save three majestic gray whales trapped under the ice of the Arctic Circle. ‘Big Miracle’ is adapted from the nonfiction book ‘Freeing the Whales: How the Media Created the World’s Greatest Non-Event’ by Tom Rose.', 'en', 8.303696, 6.6, 'Adventure Drama Romance', '', 'Drew Barrymore John Krasinski Kristen Bell'),
