(150540, 'dream cartoon imaginary friend animation family moving kids unicorn duringcreditsstinger 3d emotions', 'Inside Out', 'Growing up can be a bumpy road, and it\'s no exception for Riley, who is uprooted from her Midwest life when her father starts a new job in San Francisco. Like all of us, Riley is guided by her emotions - Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness. The emotions live in Headquarters, the control center inside Riley\'s mind, where they help advise her through everyday life. As Riley and her emotions struggle to adjust to a new life in San Francisco, turmoil ensues in Headquarters. Although Joy, Riley\'s main and most important emotion, tries to keep things positive, the emotions conflict on how best to navigate a new city, house and school.', 'en', 128.655964, 8, 'Drama Comedy Animation Family', '', 'Amy Poehler Phyllis Smith Richard Kind'),
(150689, 'cinderella magic prince fairy tale kingdom royalty orphan lost shoe evil stepmother retelling', 'Cinderella', 'When her father unexpectedly passes away, young Ella finds herself at the mercy of her cruel stepmother and her daughters. Never one to give up hope, Ella\'s fortunes begin to change after meeting a dashing stranger in the woods.', 'en', 101.187052, 6.7, 'Romance Fantasy Family Drama', '', 'Lily James Cate Blanchett Richard Madden'),
