(244786, 'jazz obsession conservatory music teacher new york city violence montage drummer public humiliation jazz band young adult music school', 'Whiplash', 'Under the direction of a ruthless instructor, a talented young drummer begins to pursue perfection at any cost, even his humanity.', 'en', 192.528841, 8.3, 'Drama', '', 'Miles Teller J.K. Simmons Melissa Benoist'),
(245700, 'painter', 'Mr. Turner', 'Eccentric British painter J.M.W. Turner  lives his last 25 years with gusto and secretly becomes involved with a seaside landlady, while his faithful housekeeper bears an unrequited love for him.', 'en', 9.242554, 6.3, 'History Drama', '', 'Timothy Spall Dorothy Atkinson Marion Bailey'),
(245703, 'father son relationship helicopter fbi motel chase child kidnapping religious sect goggles', 'Midnight Special', 'A father and son go on the run after the dad learns his child possesses special powers.', 'en', 32.717853, 6.2, 'Adventure Drama Science Fiction', '', 'Michael Shannon Jaeden Lieberher Joel Edgerton'),
(245846, 'australia missing child outback alcoholic drink troubled marriage woman director australian outback missing daughter', 'Strangerland', 'Newly arrived to a remote desert town, Catherine and Matthew are tormented by a suspicion when their two teenage children mysteriously vanish.', 'en', 5.145655, 5.1, 'Drama Thriller', '', 'Nicole Kidman Joseph Fiennes Hugo Weaving'),
(246403, 'canada obsession walrus deception search disfigurement experimental surgery abduction', 'Tusk', 'When his best friend and podcast co-host goes missing in the backwoods of Canada, a young guy joins forces with his friend\'s girlfriend to search for him.', 'en', 15.754614, 5.1, 'Comedy Horror', 'Kevin Smith', 'Michael Parks Justin Long Haley Joel Osment'),
(246655, 'mutant supernatural powers marvel comic superhero based on comic book superhuman apocalypse superhero team world domination aftercreditsstinger 1980s', 'X-Men: Apocalypse', 'After the re-emergence of the world\'s first mutant, world-destroyer Apocalypse, the X-Men must unite to defeat his extinction level plan.', 'en', 139.272042, 6.4, 'Science Fiction', '', 'James McAvoy Michael Fassbender Jennifer Lawrence'),
(248774, 'independent film woman director', 'Obvious Child', 'An immature, newly unemployed comic must navigate the murky waters of adulthood after her fling with a graduate student results in an unplanned pregnancy.', 'en', 10.12895, 6.7, 'Comedy Romance', '', 'Jenny Slate Jake Lacy Gaby Hoffmann'),
(249164, 'coma musician teenage girl car accident teenager out of body experience teen drama based on young adult novel', 'If I Stay', 'Based on Gayle Forman\'s novel of the same name. \"If I Stay\" is the story of the gifted classical musician Mia and her boyfriend, Adam, an up and coming indie-rock star. Torn between two paths in life, her art or her relationship, Mia is forced to make an even starker choice between life and death when she is caught in a fatal car accident with her family one snowy morning in Oregon.', 'en', 31.162838, 7.3, 'Drama', '', 'Chloë Grace Moretz Jamie Blackley Liana Liberato'),
(250066, 'brother brother relationship robbery bank', 'American Heist', 'Two brothers, both with troubled paths, find themselves in the middle of one last bank job.', 'en', 11.431434, 4.3, 'Action', '', 'Hayden Christensen Adrien Brody Jordana Brewster'),
(250184, 'terror anthology suspense', 'Locker 13', 'The story of Skip, a young ex-convict who takes a position as a night janitor at an old-west theme park. His supervisor Archie, teaches him the ropes, but more importantly attempts to convey critical philosophical messages through a series of four stories: a down and out boxer is given the opportunity to become a real golden gloves killer; an assassin kidnaps three people in order to find out who hired him for his latest hit; a new recruit is initiated into a lodge of fez-wearing businessmen where hazing can take a malevolent turn; and a member of a suicide club introduces real fear into a man about to jump to his death.', 'en', 1.905197, 6.8, 'Horror Drama Thriller', 'Jason Marsden', 'Ricky Schroder Jon Gries Tatyana Ali'),
(250349, '', 'Barbecue', 'On his 50th birthday, a man who\'s been watching his weight, health and temper all his life suffers a heart attack. He\'s been doing everything he was told he should do and it still didn\'t help. He decides to turn the page and let loose.', 'fr', 5.119593, 5.8, 'Comedy', 'Eric Lavaine', 'Lambert Wilson Franck Dubosc Florence Foresti'),
(250546, 'prequel evil doll killer doll spin off doll demonic possession killer toys toy comes to life', 'Annabelle', 'John Form has found the perfect gift for his expectant wife, Mia - a beautiful, rare vintage doll in a pure white wedding dress. But Mia\'s delight with Annabelle doesn\'t last long. On one horrific night, their home is invaded by members of a satanic cult, who violently attack the couple. Spilled blood and terror are not all they leave behind. The cultists have conjured an entity so malevolent that nothing they did will compare to the sinister conduit to the damned that is now... Annabelle.', 'en', 60.225219, 5.6, 'Horror', 'John R. Leonetti', 'Annabelle Wallis Ward Horton Tony Amendola'),
(250902, 'comic book biography comic book artist image comics comic book industry', 'The Image Revolution', 'Twenty years ago, seven superstar artists left Marvel Comics to create their own company, Image Comics, a company that continues to influence mainstream comics and pop culture to this day. Image began as more than just a publisher - it was a response to years of creator mistreatment, and changed comics forever. The Image Revolution tells the story of Image Comics, from its founders\' work at Marvel, through Image\'s early success, company difficulties during the comics market implosion, and ultimately the publisher\'s new generation of properties like The Walking Dead. Filled with colorful characters, the film is a clarion call to artists to take control of their destiny.', 'en', 0.54562, 5.7, 'Documentary', '', 'Todd McFarlane Rob Liefeld Jim Lee'),
(251321, 'new age woman director healer', 'Aloft', 'As we follow a mother and her son, we delve into a past marred by an accident that tears them apart. She will become a renowned artist and healer, and he will grow into his own and a peculiar falconer who bears the marks of a double absence. In the present, a young journalist will bring about an encounter between the two that puts the very meaning of life and art into question, so that we may contemplate the possibility of living life to its fullest, despite the uncertainties littering our paths.', 'en', 6.500835, 5.1, 'Drama', 'Claudia Llosa', 'Jennifer Connelly Mélanie Laurent Cillian Murphy'),
(251471, 'pop culture fan culture documentary toys', 'A LEGO Brickumentary', 'A look at the global culture and appeal of the LEGO building-block toys.', 'en', 1.631274, 6.4, 'Documentary', '', 'Jason Bateman Matthias Klie'),
(251979, 'biography christian romance', 'The Perfect Wave', '“The Perfect Wave” is the true story of Ian McCormack who grew up surfing the waters of New Zealand. Wanting to dive deeper, Ian sets out on a journey with his best friend that will change his life as they chase the perfect wave.', 'en', 4.118612, 4.4, 'Romance Adventure Drama', 'Bruce MacDonald', 'Scott Eastwood Cheryl Ladd Patrick Lyster'),
(252360, 'based on video game', 'In the Name of the King III', 'Hazen Kaine, an American contract killer living in Sofia, Bulgaria, gets more than he bargains for when he enters into a contract with the mob. One last job before he gets out and starts a new life for himself. The targets: the three children of royal billionaire Andon Dupont. Seems simple enough, or so he thought. Hazen apprehends the children, and before he can blink an eye, a simple necklace worn by one of the children sends his life spiraling back to medieval times. Now completely out of his element, Hazen fights for his life as he tries to escape a medieval army and a fierce fire-breathing dragon.', 'en', 4.304341, 3.3, 'Action Adventure Drama Fantasy', 'Uwe Boll', 'Dominic Purcell Ralitsa Paskaleva Bashar Rahal'),
(252512, 'father-in-law marriage documentary filmmaking hipster middle age documentary filmmaker generation-x generation-z psychedelic drug', 'While We\'re Young', 'An uptight documentary filmmaker and his wife find their lives loosened up a bit after befriending a free-spirited younger couple.', 'en', 19.263477, 5.8, 'Comedy Drama Mystery', 'Noah Baumbach', 'Ben Stiller Naomi Watts Adam Driver'),
(252680, 'wife husband relationship stress children mother daughter relationship parenthood parenting parent child relationship duringcreditsstinger', 'Moms\' Night Out', 'Yearning for an evening without their kids, some friends plan a night out. But to do this, their husbands need to watch the kids. What can go wrong?', 'en', 10.274542, 5.5, 'Comedy', '', 'Sarah Drew Sean Astin Patricia Heaton'),
(253235, 'grandfather granddaughter relationship neighbor wealthy elderly estrangement', 'And So It Goes', 'A self-centered realtor enlists the help of his neighbor when he\'s suddenly left in charge of the granddaughter he never knew existed until his estranged son drops her off at his home.', 'en', 9.633711, 5.7, 'Comedy Drama Romance', 'Rob Reiner', 'Michael Douglas Diane Keaton Sterling Jerins'),
(253253, '', 'Animals', 'ANIMALS tells the story of Jude and Bobbie: a young couple that exist somewhere between homelessness and the fantasy of their imaginations. Though they masterfully con and steal in an attempt to stay one step ahead of their addiction, they are ultimately forced to face the reality of their situation when one of them gets hospitalized.', 'en', 1.5846, 6.2, 'Drama', '', 'David Dastmalchian Kim Shaw John Heard'),
(253261, 'woman director', 'Born to Fly: Elizabeth Streb vs. Gravity', 'Born to Fly pushes the boundaries between action and art, daring us to join choreographer Elizabeth Streb and her dancers in pursuit of human flight.', 'en', 0.069244, 5, 'Documentary', '', 'Elizabeth Streb Fabio Tavares Sarah Callan'),
(253290, 'woman director', 'Butterfly Girl', 'Abbie came of age in honky tonks, defying her life threatening disease, but all the while longing for an identity of her own. Now that she is 18, how much is she willing to sacrifice for her independence?', 'en', 0.015189, 0, 'Documentary', 'Cary Bell', ''),
(253331, 'grieving widower widower', 'Black or White', 'A grieving widower is drawn into a custody battle over his granddaughter, whom he helped raise her entire life.', 'en', 12.172131, 6.5, 'Drama', '', 'Kevin Costner Jillian Estell Jennifer Ehle'),
(253412, 'mountains snow storm hiking climbing snow death blizzard mountain climbing based on true events mount everest 3d', 'Everest', 'Inspired by the incredible events surrounding a treacherous attempt to reach the summit of the world\'s highest mountain, \"Everest\" documents the awe-inspiring journey of two different expeditions challenged beyond their limits by one of the fiercest snowstorms ever encountered by mankind. Their mettle tested by the harshest of elements found on the planet, the climbers will face nearly impossible obstacles as a lifelong obsession becomes a breathtaking struggle for survival.', 'en', 60.246978, 6.7, 'Adventure Drama', '', 'Jason Clarke Jake Gyllenhaal Josh Brolin'),
(253626, 'pilot suspicion drone u.s. military air force base combat drone', 'Good Kill', 'In the shadowy world of drone warfare, combat unfolds like a video game–only with real lives at stake. After six tours of duty, Air Force pilot Tom Egan (Ethan Hawke) now fights the Taliban from an air-conditioned bunker in the Nevada desert. But as he yearns to get back in the cockpit of a real plane and becomes increasingly troubled by the collateral damage he causes each time he pushes a button, Egan’s nerves—and his relationship with his wife (Mad Men\'s January Jones)—begin to unravel.', 'en', 10.924273, 5.9, 'Action Drama Thriller', 'Andrew Niccol', 'Ethan Hawke January Jones Zoë Kravitz'),
(254024, 'murder investigation', 'The Face of an Angel', 'Both a journalist and a documentary filmmaker chase the story of a murder and its prime suspect.', 'en', 7.336256, 4.7, 'Thriller Drama', 'Michael Winterbottom', 'Kate Beckinsale Cara Delevingne Daniel Brühl'),
(254128, 'california earthquake catastrophe disaster film 3d san andreas san andreas california rescue operation', 'San Andreas', 'In the aftermath of a massive earthquake in California, a rescue-chopper pilot makes a dangerous journey across the state in order to rescue his estranged daughter.', 'en', 100.412364, 6, 'Action Drama Thriller', '', 'Dwayne Johnson Alexandra Daddario Carla Gugino');
INSERT INTO `movies` (`movie_id`, `tags`, `title`, `overview`, `original_language`, `popularity`, `vote_average`, `genres`, `directeur`, `acteurs`) VALUES
(254470, 'music sequel singer male female relationship audition group of friends duringcreditsstinger singing competition female musician singing contest woman director acapella', 'Pitch Perfect 2', 'The Bellas are back, and they are better than ever. After being humiliated in front of none other than the President of the United States of America, the Bellas are taken out of the Aca-Circuit. In order to clear their name, and regain their status, the Bellas take on a seemingly impossible task: winning an international competition no American team has ever won. In order to accomplish this monumental task, they need to strengthen the bonds of friendship and sisterhood and blow away the competition with their amazing aca-magic! With all new friends and old rivals tagging along for the trip, the Bellas can hopefully accomplish their dreams.', 'en', 71.496894, 6.8, 'Comedy Music', '', 'Anna Kendrick Rebel Wilson Hailee Steinfeld'),
(254472, 'giant insect', 'Stung', 'A fancy garden party turns into upper class prey when a colony of killer wasps mutates into seven foot tall predators.', 'de', 4.270489, 4.9, 'Comedy Horror', '', 'Matt O\'Leary Jessica Cook Lance Henriksen'),
(254473, 'martial arts atomic bomb ghetto parkour cops remake undercover cop gangster remake of french film', 'Brick Mansions', 'In a dystopian Detroit, grand houses that once housed the wealthy are now homes of the city\'s most-dangerous criminals. Surrounding the area is a giant wall to keep the rest of Detroit safe. For undercover cop Damien Collier, every day is a battle against corruption as he struggles to bring his father\'s killer, Tremaine, to justice. Meanwhile, Damien and an ex-con named Lino work together to save the city from a plot to destroy it.', 'en', 25.520976, 5.7, 'Action Crime Drama', '', 'Paul Walker David Belle RZA'),
(254904, 'cia retired agent', 'The November Man', 'An ex- CIA operative is brought back in on a very personal mission and finds himself pitted against his former pupil in a deadly game involving high level CIA officials and the Russian president-elect.', 'en', 45.317278, 6, 'Crime Action Thriller', '', 'Pierce Brosnan Luke Bracey Olga Kurylenko'),
(255266, 'dating divorce sex scene sex comedy anti romantic comedy', 'Dry Spell', 'Sasha tries to get her soon-to-be ex husband Kyle laid so she can move on with her sex life guilt-free.', 'en', 0.048948, 6, 'Comedy Romance', 'Travis Legge', 'Suzi Lorraine Jared Degado Heather Dorff'),
(255343, 'surfer murder murderer columbia telephone conversation', 'Escobar: Paradise Lost', 'For Pablo Escobar family is everything. When young surfer Nick falls for Escobar\'s niece, Maria, he finds his life on the line when he\'s pulled into the dangerous world of the family business.', 'en', 25.112567, 6.1, 'Thriller Romance', '', 'Benicio del Toro Josh Hutcherson Brady Corbet'),
(256040, 'kingdom war bollywood medieval india ancient india', 'Baahubali: The Beginning', 'The young Shivudu is left as a foundling in a small village by his mother. By the time he’s grown up, it has become apparent that he possesses exceptional gifts. He meets the beautiful warrior/princess Avanthika and learns that her queen has been held captive for the last 25 years. Shividu sets off to rescue her, discovering his own origins in the process.', 'te', 16.254032, 7.5, 'Action Adventure War History', 'S.S. Rajamouli', 'Prabhas Rana Daggubati Tamanna Bhatia'),
(256092, '', 'Drive Hard', 'A former race car driver is abducted by a mysterious thief and forced to be the wheel-man for a crime that puts them both in the sights of the cops and the mob.', 'en', 3.94487, 3.9, 'Action Comedy Crime', '', 'Thomas Jane John Cusack Zoe Ventoura'),
(256274, 'paris treasure catacombs scientist singing in a car archaeologist loss of friend subjective camera found footage thick accent female archeologist burning car philosopher\'s stone french accent rapping in a car', 'As Above, So Below', 'When a team of explorers ventures into the catacombs that lie beneath the streets of Paris, they uncover the dark secret that lies within this city of the dead.', 'en', 26.510558, 6.1, 'Horror Thriller', '', 'Perdita Weeks Ben Feldman Edwin Hodge'),
(256591, 'seduction con man femme fatale deception rivalry con artist', 'Focus', 'Nicky, a veteran con artist, takes a novice named Jess under his wing. While Nicky teaches Jess the tricks of the trade, the pair become romantically involved; but, when Jess gets uncomfortably close, Nicky ends their relationship. Three years later, Nicky is in Buenos Aires working a very dangerous scheme when Jess -- now an accomplished femme fatale -- unexpectedly shows up. Her appearance throws Nicky for a loop at a time when he cannot afford to be off his game.', 'en', 59.634029, 6.7, 'Romance Comedy Crime Drama', '', 'Will Smith Margot Robbie Rodrigo Santoro'),
(256687, '', 'Swelter', 'Ten years after their casino heist, four escaped convicts trace their former partner to a desert town, where he is now a lawman with no memory of his criminal past.', 'en', 2.214925, 4.6, 'Action Drama Thriller', 'Keith Parmer', 'Jean-Claude Van Damme Brad Carter Josh Henderson'),
(256740, '', 'Wicked Blood', 'Hannah and Amber Baker are trapped in a dark Southern underworld of violence, drugs and bikers. Both live in fear of their \"Uncle Frank\" Stinson, the ruthless leader of a crime organization.', 'en', 3.158056, 5.3, 'Action Drama Thriller', 'Mark Young', 'Abigail Breslin James Purefoy Sean Bean'),
(256917, 'istanbul australia post world war i farmer missing in action missing son gallipoli campaign inspired by true events', 'The Water Diviner', 'In 1919, Australian farmer Joshua Connor travels to Turkey to discover the fate of his three sons, reported missing in action. Holding on to hope, Joshua must travel across the war-torn landscape to find the truth and his own peace.', 'en', 22.096286, 6.8, 'War Drama', 'Russell Crowe', 'Russell Crowe Olga Kurylenko Yılmaz Erdoğan'),
(256924, 'rock star middle age', 'Danny Collins', 'An ageing rock star decides to change his life when he discovers a 40-year-old letter written to him by John Lennon.', 'en', 16.318608, 6.6, 'Comedy Drama Music', 'Dan Fogelman', 'Al Pacino Annette Bening Jennifer Garner'),
(256961, 'shopping mall las vegas security guard', 'Paul Blart: Mall Cop 2', 'Security guard Paul Blart is headed to Las Vegas to attend a Security Guard Expo with his teenage daughter Maya before she departs for college. While at the convention, he inadvertently discovers a heist - and it\'s up to Blart to apprehend the criminals.', 'en', 41.258487, 5, 'Action Comedy Family', '', 'Kevin James Raini Rodriguez Eduardo Verástegui'),
(256962, 'japanese world war ii spirituality', 'Little Boy', 'An eight-year-old boy is willing to do whatever it takes to end World War II so he can bring his father home. The story reveals the indescribable love a father has for his little boy and the love a son has for his father.', 'en', 12.232048, 7, 'Comedy Drama War', '', 'Jakob Salvati Emily Watson Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa'),
(257087, 'cult', 'The Veil', 'The story springs from the real-world headlines of religious cults and mass suicides. With Veil, it begins 30 years ago, when members of a religious cult known as Heaven\'s Veil take their own lives. The truth behind what really happened remains buried deep in the memory of the sole survivor, a five-year-old girl, who returns to the compound with a documentary crew as an adult. They soon discover something that is far more terrifying than anything they could have imagined.', 'en', 12.822534, 4.5, 'Horror', 'Phil Joanou', 'Jessica Alba Thomas Jane Lily Rabe'),
(257088, 'undercover undercover agent extreme sports fbi agent 3d', 'Point Break', 'A young undercover FBI agent infiltrates a gang of thieves who share a common interest in extreme sports. A remake of the 1991 film, \"Point Break\".', 'en', 33.507289, 5.5, 'Action Crime Thriller', '', 'Edgar Ramírez Luke Bracey Teresa Palmer'),
(257091, 'prison training framed embezzlement', 'Get Hard', 'When obscenely rich hedge-fund manager James is convicted of fraud and sentenced to a stretch in San Quentin, the judge gives him one month to get his affairs in order. Knowing that he won\'t survive more than a few minutes in prison on his own, James desperately turns to Darnell-- a black businessman who\'s never even had a parking ticket -- for help. As Darnell puts James through the wringer, both learn that they were wrong about many things, including each other.', 'en', 36.301202, 5.9, 'Comedy', '', 'Will Ferrell Kevin Hart Alison Brie'),
(257211, 'intern woman director', 'The Intern', '70-year-old widower Ben Whittaker has discovered that retirement isn\'t all it\'s cracked up to be. Seizing an opportunity to get back in the game, he becomes a senior intern at an online fashion site, founded and run by Jules Ostin.', 'en', 53.114573, 7.1, 'Comedy', '', 'Robert De Niro Anne Hathaway Rene Russo'),
(257344, 'video game nerd alien attack 3d pixels', 'Pixels', 'Video game experts are recruited by the military to fight 1980s-era video game characters who\'ve attacked New York.', 'en', 140.849495, 5.6, 'Action Comedy Science Fiction', 'Chris Columbus', 'Adam Sandler Michelle Monaghan Peter Dinklage'),
(257445, 'based on novel magic fantasy werewolf family ventriloquist dummy book comes to life 3d', 'Goosebumps', 'A teenager teams up with the daughter of young adult horror author R.L. Stine after the writer\'s imaginary demons are set free on the town of Madison, Delaware.', 'en', 45.351617, 6.2, 'Adventure Horror Comedy', '', 'Jack Black Dylan Minnette Odeya Rush'),
(257932, '', 'Dragon Nest: Warriors\' Dawn', 'The land of Altera has observed an uneasy peace for years among Humans, Elves and Evil beasts who are loyal to the legendary Black Dragon. But the Black Dragon begins to stir from its hibernation, sending the Beasts marching across Altera. With a beast conquest perilously close, a small group of Humans and Elves unite to try to find a secret hidden road to the Black Dragon\'s cave and destroy it. But the fate of all of them may be in the hands of the young warrior Lambert, who must summon the confidence and skill to face the Black Dragon himself just when all may be lost.', 'zh', 5.057695, 6.8, 'Adventure Family Fantasy Animation', 'Yuefeng Song', 'Carrie-Anne Moss Lucas Grabeel Blythe Auffarth'),
(258489, 'africa feral child tarzan jungle animal attack', 'The Legend of Tarzan', 'Tarzan, having acclimated to life in London, is called back to his former home in the jungle to investigate the activities at a mining encampment.', 'en', 42.741719, 5.5, 'Action Adventure', '', 'Alexander Skarsgård Margot Robbie Christoph Waltz'),
(258509, 'chipmunk cgi talking animal aftercreditsstinger duringcreditsstinger', 'Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip', 'Through a series of misunderstandings, Alvin, Simon and Theodore come to believe that Dave is going to propose to his new girlfriend in New York City - and dump them. They have three days to get to him and stop the proposal.', 'en', 27.867368, 5.8, 'Adventure Animation Comedy Family', '', 'Jason Lee Justin Long Bella Thorne'),
(259693, 'london england england 1970s spirit single mother demon paranormal investigation demonic possession valak annabelle', 'The Conjuring 2', 'Lorraine and Ed Warren travel to north London to help a single mother raising four children alone in a house plagued by malicious spirits.', 'en', 68.794673, 7, 'Horror', 'James Wan', 'Patrick Wilson Vera Farmiga Madison Wolfe'),
(259694, 'new york based on novel one-night stand single', 'How to Be Single', 'New York City is full of lonely hearts seeking the right match, and what Alice, Robin, Lucy, Meg, Tom and David all have in common is the need to learn how to be single in a world filled with ever-evolving definitions of love.', 'en', 46.078371, 5.9, 'Comedy Romance', '', 'Dakota Johnson Rebel Wilson Alison Brie'),
(259943, 'arranged marriage labor camp', 'Coming Home', 'Lu and Feng are a devoted couple forced to separate when Lu is arrested and sent to a labor camp as a political prisoner during the Cultural Revolution. He finally returns home only to find that his beloved wife no longer remembers him.', 'zh', 6.017273, 6.9, 'Drama', 'Zhang Yimou', 'Gong Li Chen Dao-Ming Guo Tao'),
(260346, 'revenge murder on the run fugitive framed father daughter relationship framed for murder', 'Taken 3', 'Ex-government operative Bryan Mills finds his life is shattered when he\'s falsely accused of a murder that hits close to home. As he\'s pursued by a savvy police inspector, Mills employs his particular set of skills to track the real killer and exact his unique brand of justice.', 'en', 88.844777, 6.1, 'Thriller Action', '', 'Liam Neeson Forest Whitaker Maggie Grace'),
(260947, 'obsession oregon independent film', 'Something Wicked', 'A young couple embark upon their honeymoon against the chilling landscapes of the Pacific Northwest. But when tragedy strikes, gruesome secrets from their past collide with sinister forces of the present...', 'en', 1.968679, 4.6, 'Mystery Thriller', '', 'Shantel VanSanten John Robinson James Patrick Stuart'),
(261023, 'boston based on true story organized crime', 'Black Mass', 'The true story of Whitey Bulger, the brother of a state senator and the most infamous violent criminal in the history of South Boston, who became an FBI informant to take down a Mafia family invading his turf.', 'en', 46.049902, 6.3, 'Crime Drama', '', 'Johnny Depp Joel Edgerton Benedict Cumberbatch'),
(262500, 'based on novel revolution dystopia sequel dystopic future young adult 3d divergent', 'Insurgent', 'Beatrice Prior must confront her inner demons and continue her fight against a powerful alliance which threatens to tear her society apart.', 'en', 103.718387, 6.2, 'Adventure Science Fiction Thriller', '', 'Shailene Woodley Theo James Kate Winslet'),
(262504, 'based on novel revolution dystopia sequel dystopic future young adult based on young adult novel', 'Allegiant', 'Beatrice Prior and Tobias Eaton venture into the world outside of the fence and are taken into protective custody by a mysterious agency known as the Bureau of Genetic Welfare.', 'en', 86.105615, 5.9, 'Adventure Science Fiction', '', 'Shailene Woodley Theo James Zoë Kravitz'),
(263503, '', 'Water & Power', 'Twin brothers nicknamed \"Water\" and \"Power\" from the hard scrabble Eastside streets of Los Angeles rise like prince\'s through the city\'s political and police ranks to become players in a complex and dangerous web of the powerful and corrupt of Los Angeles.', 'en', 0.350557, 3, 'Crime Drama', 'Richard Montoya', 'Enrique Murciano Nicholas Gonzalez Clancy Brown'),
(264644, 'based on novel carpet isolation kidnapping imprisonment grandparents escape hospital dog captive mother son relationship shed skylight', 'Room', 'Jack is a young boy of 5 years old who has lived all his life in one room. He believes everything within it are the only real things in the world. But what will happen when his Ma suddenly tells him that there are other things outside of Room?', 'en', 66.11334, 8.1, 'Drama Thriller', '', 'Brie Larson Jacob Tremblay Joan Allen'),
(264656, 'dancing based on novel revenge native american violence wild west driven insane abusive marriage refused services prison wagon lost in the desert buffalo skin', 'The Homesman', 'When three women living on the edge of the American frontier are driven mad by harsh pioneer life, the task of saving them falls to the pious, independent-minded Mary Bee Cuddy. Transporting the women by covered wagon to Iowa, she soon realizes just how daunting the journey will be, and employs a low-life drifter, George Briggs, to join her. The unlikely pair and the three women head east, where a waiting minister and his wife have offered to take the women in. But the group first must traverse the harsh Nebraska Territories marked by stark beauty, psychological peril and constant threat.', 'en', 20.59148, 6.4, 'Western Drama', '', 'Hilary Swank Tommy Lee Jones Grace Gummer'),
(264660, 'dancing artificial intelligence distrust isolation technology manipulation friendship deception laboratory robot power outage surveillance camera consciousness existentialism lockdown philosophical robot human relationship turing test cybernetics', 'Ex Machina', 'Caleb, a 26 year old coder at the world\'s largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world\'s first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.', 'en', 95.130041, 7.6, 'Drama Science Fiction', '', 'Domhnall Gleeson Alicia Vikander Oscar Isaac'),
(265208, 'gambling bodyguard remake', 'Wild Card', 'When a Las Vegas bodyguard with lethal skills and a gambling problem gets in trouble with the mob, he has one last play… and it\'s all or nothing.', 'en', 48.0343, 5.4, 'Thriller Crime Drama', '', 'Jason Statham Michael Angarano Milo Ventimiglia'),
(266102, 'dance ban from profession biography iran oppression tehran iran', 'Desert Dancer', 'Inspirational true story of Iranian dancer Afshin Ghaffarian, who risked his life for his dream to become a dancer despite a nationwide dancing ban.', 'en', 1.972668, 6.5, 'Drama', '', 'Freida Pinto Reece Ritchie Tom Cullen'),
(266396, 'assassin hitman', 'The Gunman', 'Eight years after fleeing the Congo following his assassination of that country\'s minister of mining, former assassin Jim Terrier is back, suffering from PTSD and digging wells to atone for his violent past. After an attempt is made on his life, Terrier flies to London to find out who wants him dead -- and why. Terrier\'s search leads him to a reunion with Annie, a woman he once loved, who is now married to an oily businessman with dealings in Africa.', 'en', 26.935458, 5.5, 'Action Drama Crime', '', 'Sean Penn Jasmine Trinca Javier Bardem'),
(266647, 'flying magic fairy tale peter pan mermaid pirate fantasy world', 'Pan', 'Living a bleak existence at a London orphanage, 12-year-old Peter finds himself whisked away to the fantastical world of Neverland. Adventure awaits as he meets new friend James Hook and the warrior Tiger Lily. They must band together to save Neverland from the ruthless pirate Blackbeard. Along the way, the rebellious and mischievous boy discovers his true destiny, becoming the hero forever known as Peter Pan.', 'en', 48.03528, 5.9, 'Adventure Family Fantasy', '', 'Levi Miller Garrett Hedlund Hugh Jackman'),
(266856, 'wife husband relationship biography physicist based on memoir stephen hawking fictionalized biography motor neuron disease als', 'The Theory of Everything', 'The Theory of Everything is the extraordinary story of one of the world’s greatest living minds, the renowned astrophysicist Stephen Hawking, who falls deeply in love with fellow Cambridge student Jane Wilde.', 'en', 61.182331, 7.8, 'Drama Romance', '', 'Eddie Redmayne Felicity Jones Charlie Cox'),
(266857, '', 'The Work and The Story', 'It is July, 2000 Richard Dutcher, the man who pioneered \"Mormon Cinema\" with his film \"God\'s Army\" is missing and presumed dead. Three amateur Mormon Filmmakers: Judy Shumway, Peter Beuhmann and Kevin Evans individually set out to make their first feature-length films to take Dutcher\'s place as the next \"Mormon Spielberg\". Who will win? Who will lose? Who will find Richard? And does everyone want Richard found?', 'en', 0.002388, 0, 'Comedy', 'Nathan Smith Jones', 'Kirby Heyborne Christopher Robin Miller Eric Artell'),
(267860, 'london england terrorist terrorist attack', 'London Has Fallen', 'In London for the Prime Minister\'s funeral, Mike Banning discovers a plot to assassinate all the attending world leaders.', 'en', 61.849521, 5.8, 'Action Crime Thriller', '', 'Gerard Butler Aaron Eckhart Morgan Freeman'),
(267935, 'london england england based on novel queen little girl orphan cannibal giant evil brother', 'The BFG', 'The BFG is no ordinary bone-crunching giant. He is far too nice and jumbly. It\'s lucky for Sophie that he is. Had she been carried off in the middle of the night by the Bloodbottler, or any of the other giants—rather than the BFG—she would have soon become breakfast. When Sophie hears that the giants are flush-bunking off to England to swollomp a few nice little chiddlers, she decides she must stop them once and for all. And the BFG is going to help her!', 'en', 44.19092, 6, 'Adventure Family Fantasy', 'Steven Spielberg', 'Ruby Barnhill Mark Rylance Rebecca Hall'),
(268171, 'widower', 'Elsa & Fred', 'Aged, embittered widower, Fred learns to enjoy life thanks to his elderly yet vibrant neighbor, Elsa. Upon learning Elsa is terminally ill, Fred takes her to the Fontana di Trevi in Rome in order to reenact her favorite scene from ‘La Dolce Vita’.', 'en', 2.849895, 6.2, 'Comedy Family Romance', '', 'Shirley MacLaine Christopher Plummer Chris Noth'),
(268238, 'india retirement home', 'The Second Best Exotic Marigold Hotel', 'As the Best Exotic Marigold Hotel has only a single remaining vacancy - posing a rooming predicament for two fresh arrivals - Sonny pursues his expansionist dream of opening a second hotel.', 'en', 17.592299, 6.3, 'Drama Comedy', 'John Madden', 'Dev Patel Judi Dench Richard Gere'),
(268917, 'artist band', 'The Past Is a Grotesque Animal', 'A personal, accessible look at an artist - Kevin Barnes, frontman of the endlessly versatile indie pop band of Montreal - whose pursuit to make transcendent music at all costs drives him to value art over human relationships. As he struggles with all of those around him, family and bandmates alike, he\'s forced to reconsider the future of the band, begging the question - is this really worth it?', 'en', 0.394575, 5.5, 'Documentary Music', 'Jason Miller', 'Dottie Alexander Derek Almstead David Barnes'),
(268920, 'texas prisoner cop drug cartel on the run police officer prisoner on the run woman director', 'Hot Pursuit', 'An uptight by-the-book cop must protect the widow of a drug boss from crooked cops and gunmen.', 'en', 18.262017, 5.4, 'Action Comedy Crime', '', 'Reese Witherspoon Sofía Vergara Michael Mosley'),
(270303, 'chase supernatural friends vision school young adult followed', 'It Follows', 'For 19-year-old Jay, fall should be about school, boys and weekends out at the lake. But a seemingly innocent physical encounter turns sour and gives her the inescapable sense that someone, or something, is following her. Faced with this burden, Jay and her teenage friends must find a way to escape the horror that seems to be only a few steps behind.', 'en', 100.876794, 6.6, 'Horror Thriller', '', 'Maika Monroe Keir Gilchrist Daniel Zovatto'),
(270487, 'journalist cat ransom kidnapping ancient rome movie in movie hollywood period drama', 'Hail, Caesar!', 'Tells the comedic tale of Eddie Mannix, a fixer who worked for the Hollywood studios in the 1950s. The story finds him at work when a star mysteriously disappears in the middle of filming.', 'en', 39.006187, 5.7, 'Comedy Drama Mystery', 'Joel Coen', 'Josh Brolin George Clooney Alden Ehrenreich'),
