(272693, 'high school teenager popularity high school student teen comedy duringcreditsstinger girl next door based on young adult novel', 'The DUFF', 'Bianca\'s universe turns upside down when she learns that her high school refers to her as a ‘DUFF\' (Designated Ugly Fat Friend). Hoping to erase that label, she enlists the help of a charming jock and her favorite teacher. Together they\'ll face the school\'s mean girl and remind everyone that we are all someone\'s DUFF… and that\'s totally fine.', 'en', 40.28709, 6.8, 'Romance Comedy', '', 'Mae Whitman Robbie Amell Bella Thorne'),
