(283708, 'fire classroom hostage rain horse rifle children teacher school rural setting school teacher based on short story algeria journey 1950s algerian war mountain', 'Far from Men', 'A French teacher in a small Algerian village during the Algerian War forms an unexpected bond with a dissident who is ordered to be turned in to the authorities.', 'fr', 3.363973, 6.6, 'Drama War', '', 'Viggo Mortensen Reda Kateb Djemel Barek'),
